<p class="text-justify">(d)	in line with the Fair Work (Commonwealth Powers) Act 2009, Fair Work Act 2009, Labour Hire Licensing Act 2018 (VIC) and other laws regulations, Candidates are required to a paid break when working five (5) hours or more (as per the applicable award rates) – billing will continue during this time.</p>
